"Config file for vimperator for Adrian Bradd

"Use sane hintchars and reasonable colours
set hintchars=hsdfgyuiopqwertnmzxcvb
highlight Hint font-size:100%;color:white;background-color:black;padding:2px;

"Make the command line a larger font so that it can be read
highlight CmdLine -append font-size:16px;
highlight CompTitle -append font-size:16px;
highlight CompResult -append font-size:16px;
highlight CompDesc -append font-size:16px;

"gt and gT sucks for tab navigation
nmap K gt
nmap J gT
